%% Sequence Diagram - User Navigation Flow
%% Render with: https://mermaid.live or VS Code Mermaid extension

sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant B as Browser
    participant V as Vite Dev Server
    participant R as React App
    participant E as External APIs

    Note over U,E: Initial Page Load
    U->>B: Navigate to site
    B->>V: GET /index.html
    V->>B: HTML + JS bundle
    B->>E: Load Google Fonts
    B->>R: Mount React root
    R->>B: Render all sections (SPA)
    B->>U: Display portfolio

    Note over U,E: Navigation
    U->>B: Click nav link (#about)
    B->>B: Smooth scroll to section
    B->>R: Navbar detects scroll position
    R->>B: Update navbar background (blur)

    Note over U,E: Mobile Navigation
    U->>B: Click hamburger menu
    R->>B: Toggle mobile menu overlay
    U->>B: Click nav link
    R->>B: Close menu + scroll to section

    Note over U,E: Contact (Future)
    U->>B: Fill contact form
    B->>R: Form state update
    U->>B: Submit form
    R->>E: POST to EmailJS/Formspree
    E->>R: Success response
    R->>B: Show confirmation message

    Note over U,E: Blog (Future)
    U->>B: Navigate to blog
    R->>E: Fetch posts from CMS API
    E->>R: Return blog posts JSON
    R->>B: Render blog listing
